title: ‘Andor’ Episode 6, ‘The Midnight Club,’ and ‘High School’
description:
Chris and Andy talk about how this latest episode of ‘Andor’ might have been the best hour of 'Star Wars' in years (1:00). Then they hit on all of the ’90s needle drops in the newest Mike Flanagan show ‘The Midnight Club’ (32:28) and the teen drama show from Tegan and Sara, ‘High School’ (41:01).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Producer: Kaya McMullen
